sequenceDiagram
    participant OS as OS 커널
    participant AL as AcceptLoop
    participant SM as SessionManager
    participant AP as AsyncIOProvider
    participant LD as KeyedDispatcher

    Note over AL: StartPlatformIO() 이후<br/>전담 accept 스레드에서 실행

    OS -->> AL: accept() 완료 (clientSocket)
    AL ->> SM: CreateSession(clientSocket)
    SM -->> AL: SessionRef
    AL ->> AP: AssociateSocket(socket, connectionId)
    Note over AP: IOCP: CreateIoCompletionPort<br/>epoll: EPOLL_CTL_ADD<br/>kqueue: kevent EV_ADD
    AP -->> AL: AsyncIOError::Success
    AL ->> AP: RecvAsync(socket, buffer, context)
    AP -->> AL: OperationPending

    AL ->> LD: Dispatch(sessionId, OnConnected + FireEvent)
    Note over LD: 동일 sessionId → 단일 워커 직렬화<br/>FIFO 순서 보장

    loop I/O 완료 이벤트 루프 (워커 스레드)
        OS -->> AP: I/O 완료 신호
        AP -->> AL: CompletionEntry[0..63]
        AL ->> AL: ProcessCompletions()
        alt AsyncIOType::Recv (bytesReceived > 0)
            AL ->> LD: Dispatch(sessionId, ProcessRecvCompletion)
        else AsyncIOType::Send
            AL ->> LD: Dispatch(sessionId, ProcessSendCompletion)
        else 에러 또는 result <= 0
            AL ->> LD: Dispatch(sessionId, ProcessErrorCompletion)
            LD ->> LD: FireEvent(Disconnected)
            LD ->> SM: RemoveSession(sessionId)
        end
        AL ->> AP: RecvAsync(socket, buffer, context)
        Note over AP: 다음 수신 작업 투입
    end
